{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1784190023879,"sessionID":"ses_09619781bffeQ3oAZ5RFeTTgCJ","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_160d950c99a64189adf3835d","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Deep Research Dashboard — glm52-max lineage\n\n> Auto-generated operator summary. Not manually edited.\n\n## Iteration Table\n\n| run | focus | newInfoRatio | findings | status |\n|-----|-------|--------------|----------|--------|\n| 1 | RQ1 workflow-YAML schema + corpus divergence | 1.0 | 5 | complete |\n| 2 | RQ2 presentation ownership + typed inline-exception | 0.78 | 5 | complete |\n| 3 | RQ3 mode completeness + mode matrix | 0.8 | 5 | complete |\n| 4 | RQ4 route-manifest YAMLs + executable-edge cycle parsing | 0.82 | 5 | complete |\n| 5 | RQ5 generation/ergonomics + fat-router decomposition + backlog | 0.6 | 5 | complete |\n\n## Question Status: 5/5 answered\n\n| RQ | Status |\n|----|--------|\n| RQ1 — Workflow-YAML schema + divergence | answered (D1.1–D1.5; schema + confirm==auto+checkpoints; 20/15 split) |\n| RQ2 — Presentation ownership + typed exception | answered (D2.1–D2.5; memory/search render-fidelity exception) |\n| RQ3 — Mode completeness + mode matrix | answered (D3.1–D3.5; two-sided matrix-gated check) |\n| RQ4 — Route-manifest + cycle parsing | answered (D4.1–D4.5; AL4 PROVEN with smoking-gun comments) |\n| RQ5 — Generation + ergonomics | answered (D5.1–D5.3; render-from-contract + deep fat-router) |\n\n## Convergence Trend\n\nnewInfoRatio: 1.0 → 0.78 → 0.8 → 0.82 → 0.6 (avg 0.80). No early convergence — forced non-convergence held (stopPolicy max-iterations; convergence telemetry-only).\n\n## AL Defect → Backlog Coverage\n\n| AL defect | Backlog delta | Tier |\n|-----------|---------------|------|\n| AL1 mode-completeness unchecked | A-W1 | W |\n| AL2 mode-default policy invisible | A-K2 / A-W4 | K/W |\n| AL3 presentation ownership untyped | A-K2 / A-W3 | K/W |\n| AL4 YAML comments misread as edges | A-K1 (keystone) | K |\n| AL5 doctor route-manifest unnamed | A-W2 | W |\n| AL6 .txt ownership labels wrong | A-G3 | G |\n\n## Keystones\n\n- **A-K1** — Executable-edge cycle parsing (AL4 proven; unblocks trusting 066 P0 cycle findings).\n- **A-K2** — Typed command contract + workflow-YAML schema (the data the rest renders from).\n\n## Dead Ends / Ruled Out\n\n- Rewrite the YAMLs to a new schema (triad is validated-good).\n- Hardcode an inline-tolerant allowlist (preserves the regeneration defect).\n- Force both :auto/:confirm on every router (contradicts doctor/memory).\n- Strip all `#` globally before extraction (corrupts code anchors/prose).\n- Slim deep/* routers by hand before the contract (A7 anti-pattern).\n\n## Blocked Stops\n\nNone. Stop reason: `maxIterationsReached` (stopPolicy max-iterations; convergence telemetry-only by design).\n\n## Next Focus\n\nSynthesis complete. Canonical synthesis written to `research.md`. Hand-off: parent session cross-reconciles glm52-max with the `gpt56-sol-xhigh-fast` sibling lineage, then seeds follow-on asset-layer remediation packets from the A-K/A-W/A-G backlog — start with A-K1 (cycle parser, independent) and A-K2 (contract), per the dependency spine `A-K1 ∥ A-K2 → (A-W1..A-W4) → A-G1 → (A-G2, A-G3)`.\n","filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/066-command-surface-benchmark/014-command-asset-layer-research/research/lineages/glm52-max/deep-research-dashboard.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/066-command-surface-benchmark/014-command-asset-layer-research/research/lineages/glm52-max/deep-research-dashboard.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/system-deep-loop/066-command-surface-benchmark/014-command-asset-layer-research/research/lineages/glm52-max/deep-research-dashboard.md","time":{"start":1784190023873,"end":1784